{"tid":1163934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔識點同屋企人相處","createTime":"2019-05-20T17:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T01:05:10.000Z","uid":220372,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e52bbda1b7fa85c70c735ed2925ecc55537761d3","tid":1163934,"uid":220372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:48:06.000Z","msg":"比阿媽鬧我對屋企人好冷淡，好似陌生人咁，唔同屋企人傾計行街。<br />\n但自問成日幫屋企整呢樣整嗰樣，得閒冇事都會請兩老食飯，絕對唔係唔鐘意屋企。我只係唔鐘意講嘢同唔識表達啫... 點解佢唔明......<br />\n前兩日佢同我嘈咗一輪，我都講哂我對屋企根本唔係冇付出，我只係唔鐘意講嘢，但佢都好似唔明咁，仲話佢供書交學咁多年，我都唔好好關心佢。<br />\n啱啱成家人訓哂，佢突然大嗌、尖叫、喊，發噩夢。我都幾肯定佢係因為同我嘈交搞到咁，其實好心up.... <br />\n我都唔想搞到大家咁樣.... 我可以點做好.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a91567cf9c15a7d9b707f4628360a3b2ed069d","tid":1163934,"uid":254259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"687da0b61e4014f91db081dcf04b9fbfeaab02e0","tid":1163934,"uid":220372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3a91567cf9c15a7d9b707f4628360a3b2ed069d","tid":1163934,"uid":254259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"下星期開始有成個月唔喺屋企，可能真係要分開一下先得...."},{"pid":"d63eacd02e4bf0ddc234d2e7c0db2534bb4f035e","tid":1163934,"uid":88273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"真係要珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0656da1779649e28389d59c3ea392816e21e6bd9","tid":1163934,"uid":35324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d63eacd02e4bf0ddc234d2e7c0db2534bb4f035e","tid":1163934,"uid":88273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"真係要珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"你咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb14f772